Program: Outlook
Title: 27/07/2011
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00j0kzl
Last Broadcast Date: Thu 28 Jul 2011
Extraordinary personal stories from around the world. Today, the terrible ordeal of British couple Bill and Julia Hawker. Their 22 year old daughter Lindsay was raped and murdered in Japan in 2007. They put their lives on hold to try and track down her killer. And our man in Pakistan's Swat valley, Adnan Rashid reflects on the first anniversary of the floods that devastated the region. Show less